findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function massUpdatePools() uses a loop to update all pools which may cause out of gas issue if array length is too big.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges including setting treasury address, withdrawing BNB, adding pool and grave, incrementing launch phase of zombie contract, changing various parameters, and minting extra zombieReward to dev address.
